Project:
Insta Post → Screenshot → Share → Send it to our app → Goes to app → Something will parse it (Some sort of LLM) → Any parts not filled out, you fill out yourself → Block on calendar → Notify you based on your calendar in your app 

Tech Stack:
Web Server - Vercel
LLM - Snowflake / Featherless 
Front End - Node.js, react
Backend - Python (collect data about emails, passwords, info about them) , SUPA base? 

